Our manager is Mr. Schoen, but he's not in today.

8
00:02:02,734 --> 00:02:05,653
-你看到那個帶手提箱的人？ -是
-But you see the man with the briefcase. -Yes.

9
00:02:05,736 --> 00:02:08,029
