- You tell Buddy-- - Okay, all right, and the guy driving the other car?

85
00:09:05,407 --> 00:09:09,660
- 哪個？ - 因為你老搞不定車子
- What are you talking about? - Well, seeing as you have so much luck with cars,

86
00:09:09,745 --> 00:09:12,455
