89
00:09:17,585 --> 00:09:21,463
是他，巴蒂說葛蘭認為你們這一夥真酷
Uh-huh, that's him. Buddy said Glenn thinks you guys are real cool.

90
00:09:21,505 --> 00:09:23,465
- 阿黛爾？ - 呀？
- Adele? - Yeah?

91
00:09:23,507 --> 00:09:27,844
告訴巴蒂如果葛蘭戴太陽眼鏡，我就踩爛他
You tell Buddy l see Glenn wearing his sunglasses, I'm gonna step on 'em.

92
00:09:27,928 --> 00:09:31,097
- 我甚至一開始就不拿下來 - 好的，我會的
- Might not even take 'em off first. - Okay, honey. l'll do that.

93
00:09:31,139 --> 00:09:33,307
小心不要被射死，拜拜。
Now, you try not to get shot. Bye.

94
00:09:33,474 --> 00:09:35,434
嗨
Hey--

95
00:09:57,246 --> 00:09:59,706
