We don't talk much anymore.

127
00:11:58,689 --> 00:12:03,151
我星期天過來，一起看超級杯？
How 'bout l come over Sunday and we watch the Super Bowl together?

128
00:12:03,235 --> 00:12:05,195
太好了
l'd like that.

129
00:12:06,279 --> 00:12:08,113
