I don't hear anything. Where's the tunnel come out?

132
00:12:31,135 --> 00:12:33,970
從守望塔第四根柱子
Fourth post from the guard tower.

133
00:12:34,054 --> 00:12:36,264
我什麼也沒看見
I don't see nothin'.

134
00:12:36,306 --> 00:12:38,266
繼續看
You just keep watchin'.

135
00:13:00,495 --> 00:13:03,122
聯邦調查局，請問找哪位？
Federal Bureau of lnvestigation, how may l direct your call?

136
00:13:03,164 --> 00:13:05,707
我是凱倫西斯柯，找雷尼可
Yeah, this is Karen Sisco again for Ray Nicolet.

137
00:13:05,791 --> 00:13:07,876
