153
00:15:30,464 --> 00:15:34,634
- 別緊張，我們是好人 - 你在這裡幹什麼？
- It's okay, we're the good guys. - What are you doing here?

154
00:15:34,717 --> 00:15:38,637
她只是個女孩，為什麼用槍？
All right. You're just a girl. What do you do for a living you pack a shotgun?

155
00:15:38,679 --> 00:15:43,516
- 我是聯邦警察，你被捕了！ - 可能都是
- I'm a federal marshal and you're under arrest. - That's probably all the hacks.

156
00:15:43,600 --> 00:15:45,977
我們等會再說吧
Why don't we talk about this later?

157
00:15:47,604 --> 00:15:49,522
小心你的頭
Watch your head.

158
00:15:49,606 --> 00:15:51,274
我進來了，走吧
I'm in. Let's go!

159
00:15:53,151 --> 00:15:56,987
- 你舒服嗎？ - 太擠了
- Hey! You comfy? - lf l could have a little more room--

160
00:15:57,071 --> 00:15:58,989
沒地方了
Well, there isn't any.

161
00:15:59,073 --> 00:16:02,117
這裡有好東西，手銬啊
We got a lot of shit in here. We got handcuffs in here.

162
00:16:02,159 --> 00:16:04,786
這罐子裡是什麼？
What's in this can?

163
00:16:04,828 --> 00:16:07,789
除口臭的，擠一點到你嘴巴裡
That's for your breath. You could use it-- squirt some in your mouth.

164
00:16:07,831 --> 00:16:09,832
那是美斯，不是嗎？
Yeah, well, that's mace, isn't it?

165
00:16:16,547 --> 00:16:19,591
好吧！你，去……
All right, you! Get--

166
00:16:21,677 --> 00:16:25,513
嘿，你的槍呢？你的手槍
Hey. Where's your gun-- pistol?

167
00:16:25,555 --> 00:16:28,641
在車裡，我的包裡
ln my bag, in the car.

168
00:16:39,026 --> 00:16:40,986
要命，這裡真臭
Boy, it stunk in there.

169
00:16:41,027 --> 00:16:44,822
我想是的，你把我爸給我的值900元的套裝弄壞了
l believe it. You're ruining a $900 suit my dad gave me.

170
00:16:44,864 --> 00:16:47,449
它和那只12口徑的槍很配
Yeah, it went great with that 12-gauge too.

171
00:16:47,533 --> 00:16:49,785
像你這種人怎麼會當法警
Why in the world would someone like you become a federal marshal?

172
00:16:49,869 --> 00:16:52,871
- 專門抓你這種人 - 那是什麼意思？
- The idea of going after guys like you appealed to me. - Sorry, what was that?

173
00:16:52,955 --> 00:16:55,081
像我這種人！讓我告訴你吧
Guys like me? Let me tell you something.

174
00:16:55,165 --> 00:16:58,376
雖然我近來單身，但是我不是非要纏著你不可
Even though l've been celibate lately, I'm not going to force myself on you.

175
00:16:58,460 --> 00:17:01,087
- 我從沒做過 - 你不會有時間做
- l've never done that in my life. - You wouldn't have time, anyway.

176
00:17:01,171 --> 00:17:04,549
碰到路障，他們查車後就會知道這是誰的車了
We come to a roadblock, they run the car and find out who it belongs to.

177
00:17:04,632 --> 00:17:07,926
即使他們要設的話，我懷疑他們能否及時設一個
That's if they get set up in time, which l doubt. lf they do,

178
00:17:08,010 --> 00:17:12,013
他們要找兩個拉丁人，而不是個黑大個.
they'll be lookin' for a bunch of little Latin fellas, not a big black guy drivin' a Ford.

179
00:17:12,055 --> 00:17:15,224
他真是你的好兄弟，如此拿自己來犧牲
He must be quite a pal, to risk his own ass like this.

180
00:17:15,267 --> 00:17:17,310
巴蒂，他是個好傢伙
Buddy? Yeah, he's a good guy.

181
00:17:17,394 --> 00:17:22,607
我們一起坐牢時，他每週一定打電話給他姐姐
Back when we jailed together, he used to call his sister every week, without fail.

182
00:17:22,690 --> 00:17:26,401
她是重生的基督徒，給電視布道家記賬
She's a born-again Christian. She does bookkeeping for a televangelist.

183
00:17:26,485 --> 00:17:28,403
他會打電話向她懺悔
He'd call her up, confess his sins.

184
00:17:28,487 --> 00:17:30,739
告訴他搶過的銀行
He'd tell her whatever bank he happened to rob at the time.

185
00:17:30,822 --> 00:17:32,907
巴蒂是他的名字嗎？
Buddy-- that his given name?

186
00:17:32,991 --> 00:17:35,409
對！我給他取得
The one l gave him, yeah.

187
00:17:35,493 --> 00:17:38,745
你叫什麼？
So, what's your name?

188
00:17:38,830 --> 00:17:41,248
明天看報就知道了
Be in the paper tomorrow, anyway.

189
00:17:41,290 --> 00:17:44,542
傑克弗裡，你恐怕聽過
Jack Foley. You've probably heard of me.

190
00:17:44,585 --> 00:17:47,837
-為什麼，你很有名嗎？ -我在加州被判刑時
-Why? Are you famous? -The time l was convicted in California,

191
00:17:47,921 --> 00:17:52,842
調查局說我搶銀行的紀錄比誰都多
the F.B.l. told me that l'd robbed more banks than anybody in the computer.

192
00:17:52,926 --> 00:17:55,595
- 多少次？ - 我真的不知道
- How many was that? - Tell you the truth, I don't really know.

193
00:17:55,636 --> 00:18:01,057
我18歲時開始替我叔叔卡利和他搭檔開車
Started when l was 18 years old, driving for my Uncle Cully, and his partner, Gus.

194
00:18:01,100 --> 00:18:05,729
你是說你半輩子都在牢裡
So, basically you're saying you spent half your life in prison.

195
00:18:05,771 --> 00:18:08,440
對，如果再被逮住，要關30年
Basically, yeah. l go back, l do 30 years. No time off.

196
00:18:08,523 --> 00:18:13,569
- 你能想像嗎？ - 我不用想，我又不搶銀行
- You imagine lookin' at that? - I don't have to. I don't rob banks.

197
00:18:16,197 --> 00:18:18,115
你好像一點都不怕
You don't seem all that scared.

198
00:18:18,199 --> 00:18:21,952
- 我當然怕 - 看不出來
- Of course l am. - You don't act like it.

199
00:18:21,994 --> 00:18:23,954
你要我大叫嗎？
What do you want me to do, scream?

200
00:18:23,995 --> 00:18:26,121
那也起不了作用
That wouldn't help much, anyway.

201
00:18:26,164 --> 00:18:31,835
我打算坐在這裡，等你自己搞砸
No, I'm just gonna sit here, take it easy, and wait for you to screw up.

202
00:18:31,919 --> 00:18:34,296
聽起來像我前妻
You sound like my ex-wife.

203
00:18:34,338 --> 00:18:38,800
- 你結過婚 - 一年左右
- You were married? - Just for about a year, give or take a few days.

204
00:18:38,884 --> 00:18:41,761
我們相處得不錯，只是……
It's not like we didn't get along-- we had fun. We just...

205
00:18:41,803 --> 00:18:45,431
沒有那種……
didn't have... that thing, you know, that uh--

206
00:18:45,473 --> 00:18:50,269
- 激情，那很重要 - 嗯哼
- That spark, you know? Gotta have that. - Mm-hmm.

207
00:18:50,311 --> 00:18:52,646
- 儘管我們仍在說話 - 是嗎？
- We still talk, though. - Sure.

208
00:18:55,524 --> 00:18:58,151
你是不會有好下場的 做這種事永遠都不會有
This is not gonna end well. These things never do.

209
00:18:58,193 --> 00:19:00,987
我要死也想被人打死在大街上
lf it turns out l get shot like a dog, it's gonna be in the street,

210
00:19:01,071 --> 00:19:03,156
不想死在牢裡
not off a goddamn fence.

211
00:19:03,198 --> 00:19:06,867
你真以為你是什麼克萊貝羅
You must really see yourself as some kind of Clyde Barrow, huh?

212
00:19:11,455 --> 00:19:14,332
- 你是指邦尼和克萊 - 是的
- You mean, of Bonnie and Clyde? - Yeah.

213
00:19:18,044 --> 00:19:21,797
電影中他們中彈 華倫比提和……
The part in the movie where they get shot, when it's Warren Beatty and--

214
00:19:21,839 --> 00:19:24,382
- 費唐 娜薇 - 費唐 娜薇，yeah.
- Faye Dunaway. - Faye Dunaway, yeah.

215
00:19:24,467 --> 00:19:28,720
- 我喜歡她演的「電視網」 - 演得真好
- l like her in that movie about TV. - Network, yeah, she was good.

216
00:19:28,804 --> 00:19:31,890
那傢伙說他再不吃那套
And that guy says he's not gonna take any more shit from anybody.

217
00:19:31,974 --> 00:19:34,559
- 彼特 芬奇 - Yeah! 彼特 芬奇
- Peter Finch. - Yeah! Peter Finch.

218
00:19:34,643 --> 00:19:38,688
「我已經火大了，我不會吃你那套」
''I'm mad as hell, and I'm not gonna take any more of your shit!''

219
00:19:41,149 --> 00:19:43,484
在他們中槍的那一節，我記得我一直在想……
ln that part where they get shot, l can remember thinkin' to myself,

220
00:19:43,526 --> 00:19:48,739
如果你別無選擇的時候，這個結局也不算太壞
thinkin', ''Hey, that wouldn't be such a bad way to go, if you had to.''

221
00:20:08,965 --> 00:20:10,883
你很會和人聊天
You sure are easy to talk to.

222
00:20:14,971 --> 00:20:19,850
如果我們在不同的場合下遇到
l was thinkin', if we met under different circumstances--

223
00:20:19,892 --> 00:20:23,561
你在酒吧，我出現，我們交談
if you were in a bar and l came up and we started talkin'--

224
00:20:23,604 --> 00:20:26,189
- 然後呢？ - 沒有了
- l wonder what would happen. - Nothing.

225
00:20:26,231 --> 00:20:29,400
- 如果你不知道我是誰 - 你可能會告訴我
- lf you didn't know who l was. - You'd probably tell me.

226
00:20:29,442 --> 00:20:32,653
- 如果場合不同…… - 你在開玩笑
- Just saying if we met under different circumstances-- - You have got to be kidding.

227
00:20:32,737 --> 00:20:35,698
是, 是
Yeah. Yeah.

228
00:20:35,740 --> 00:20:40,619
我喜歡另一部費唐娜薇演的電影是《三日兀鷹》
Another movie l liked with Faye Dunaway was Three Days of the Condor.

229
00:20:40,702 --> 00:20:43,371
勞伯瑞夫年輕時拍的那部
The one with Robert Redford when he was young.

230
00:20:43,413 --> 00:20:45,373
是
Yeah.

231
00:20:47,500 --> 00:20:50,669
那部電影一點意思都沒有
You know, l never thought it made sense, though--

232
00:20:50,753 --> 00:20:53,755
他們那麼快就好上了
you know, the way they got together so quick.

233
00:20:53,798 --> 00:20:55,758
是嘛？
Why not?

234
00:20:55,799 --> 00:20:58,092
- 很浪漫 - 嗯哼
- l mean, romantically. - Mm-hmm.

235
00:21:01,096 --> 00:21:04,765
可是……
Well, but it-- if-- uh. All right.

236
00:21:05,308 --> 00:21:07,935
又停了。 我們現在在哪裡?
Here we go. All right. Where the hell are we?

237
00:21:07,977 --> 00:21:09,978
公路收費口，葛蘭在上面另一輛車裡
At the turnpike. Glenn's right above us with the other car.

238
00:21:10,062 --> 00:21:13,064
- 快出來! - 背過身舉起手
- All right, c'mon. Hop on out. - Turn around and get your hands up!

239
00:21:13,107 --> 00:21:15,192
快出來!背過身舉起手
Shit!

240
00:21:15,275 --> 00:21:17,485
別管她，反正我們也不要這輛車了
We may as well leave her. We're leavin' the car...

241
00:21:17,569 --> 00:21:19,320
我們總要把她甩了
and we gotta leave her someplace, anyway-- what's the difference where?

242
00:21:19,404 --> 00:21:22,281
- 她得跟著我們。 - 天啊，你在那裡搞什麼?
- She's comin' with us. - Jesus Christ, what were you doing in there?

243
00:21:22,365 --> 00:21:25,242
- 找名字 - 找過了
- Look for a name. - l already looked.

244
00:21:25,284 --> 00:21:28,620
她叫凱倫西思科，像席司科孩童，拼法不同
Her name is Karen Sisco. Like the Cisco Kid, only spelled different.

245
00:21:28,662 --> 00:21:30,788
S-l-S-C-O.
S-l-S-C-O.

246
00:21:35,460 --> 00:21:37,378
Karen?
Karen?

247
00:21:37,462 --> 00:21:40,673
凱倫，你要老實一點
All right, Karen? You be a good girl, now.

248
00:21:40,757 --> 00:21:42,800
我要打開後車蓋了
I'm gonna open up the trunk.

249
00:21:42,842 --> 00:21:47,137
喂! 喂! 喂! 你在往自己車上打窟窿
Hey, hey, hey, now! Now, you're puttin' holes in your car!

250
00:21:47,179 --> 00:21:53,017
我不會把你扔在這裡， 我要開後車蓋，你把槍扔出來。
I'm not leavin' you. I'm gonna open the trunk enough for you to drop your pistol out.

251
00:21:53,101 --> 00:21:56,729
巴蒂有你的獵槍， 你要開槍的話，他會射回去
Now, if you shoot, Buddy's got your shotgun, he's gonna shoot back.

252
00:21:56,813 --> 00:21:59,648
我攔不住他，就看你自己了
There's nothin' l can do about it, so it's up to you.

253
00:21:59,732 --> 00:22:04,653
別開槍!是葛蘭
Hey. Don't! It's Glenn! Whoa!

254
00:22:04,737 --> 00:22:08,198
媽的，傑克，很高興見到你
Fuck! Hey, hey, Jack. Good to see you, man.

255
00:22:08,281 --> 00:22:11,659
你們在射誰?
What the fuck are you guys shooting at?

256
00:22:11,701 --> 00:22:13,911
- 我們要他嗎? - 警察見過這輛車
- Do we need 'im? - The cop saw this car.

257
00:22:13,995 --> 00:22:16,956
- 他可能會起疑心再調回頭 - 好吧
- He might tie it to the break and turn around. - All right.

258
00:22:16,998 --> 00:22:21,543
- 嘿，小伙子，我們沒認出你 - 嘿，「小伙子。」
- Hey, Studs. We didn't recognize ya. - Hey, ''Studs,'' man.

259
00:22:21,627 --> 00:22:26,714
從蘭坡出來後就沒有聽過混得怎麼樣?
l haven't heard that since Lompoc, man. So what's goin' on?

260
00:22:28,049 --> 00:22:30,009
沒怎麼樣
Aw, nothin'.

261
00:22:31,052 --> 00:22:35,055
凱倫，你要出來嗎?
Karen. Are you comin' out?

262
00:22:38,350 --> 00:22:41,060
- 聽到了嗎？ - 好吧。
- You hear that? - Okay!

263
00:22:42,354 --> 00:22:44,314
—聽到了嗎？好吧。
Okay.

264
00:22:52,530 --> 00:22:54,490
算你贏，傑克
You win, Jack.

265
00:23:05,375 --> 00:23:07,918
衣服乾洗完後 帳單寄給我
Now, you get your clothes cleaned, you send me the bill.

266
00:23:08,002 --> 00:23:09,962
我會寄到葛雷茲去
l'll send it to you at Glades.

267
00:23:10,046 --> 00:23:13,382
你是不是剛從陰溝洞裡爬出來?你是誰?
What, did you crawl through a sewer, man? Who're you?

268
00:23:13,424 --> 00:23:16,843
- 摘下墨鏡 - 戴著看得更清楚
- Take your sunglasses off. - l see better with 'em on, man.

269
00:23:16,885 --> 00:23:19,178
小心我把你和墨鏡一起扔到天橋上去
You don't take 'em off I'm gonna throw them off while they're still on your head.

270
00:23:19,221 --> 00:23:24,392
- 等在車裡 - 文明社會裡，說話客氣點
- Go wait in the car. - Um, we're in civilization now, so you can ease up a little bit.

271
00:23:24,434 --> 00:23:28,687
對不起，請你在車裡等，帶上她，放在後座!
I'm sorry. l'd like you to wait in the car, please. Take her, put her in the back.

272
00:23:28,729 --> 00:23:32,690
- 後車廂？後坐！
- Okay. ln the trunk? - ln the backseat! ln the backseat!

273
00:23:32,733 --> 00:23:36,111
- 過來!因為我要…… - 把外套給我!
- Backseat. Okay, you gotta come now, 'cause l gotta do this-- - Gimme your jacket.

274
00:23:36,194 --> 00:23:38,571
我需要乾淨衣服
Somebody forgot to bring the clean clothes.

275
00:23:38,613 --> 00:23:40,698
乾淨衣服在凱迪拉克車裡
l brought 'em. They're at Glades in the back of the Cadillac.

276
00:23:40,740 --> 00:23:43,075
是你自己要跳進她的後車箱
You decided to jump into the trunk of her car.

277
00:23:43,159 --> 00:23:45,702
你可以怪我，我不介意
You can blame me if you want. I don't mind.

278
00:23:45,745 --> 00:23:49,414
—給你：我要告訴你……
- Here, sir. - l'll tell you--

279
00:23:49,456 --> 00:23:52,041
- 你有什麼毛病? - 你為什麼叫葛蘭來
- What's your problem, Jack? - I don't know why you got Glenn involved in this.

280
00:23:52,084 --> 00:23:54,419
- 這件事是他的主意 - 他?
- How 'bout the score was his idea to begin with? - ldea--

281
00:23:54,502 --> 00:23:56,587
他沒有大腦的
The guy's got a fuckin' vacant lot for a head.

282
00:23:56,629 --> 00:24:00,590
他以為他可以用這種口氣跟我說話
He thinks he can talk to me like that? Shit.

283
00:24:00,633 --> 00:24:05,595
「把外套給我」我坐在這裡等了半個鐘頭
''Gimme your jacket.'' l have been sitting here for over a half-hour,

284
00:24:05,638 --> 00:24:09,433
防備著警察。你以為那是好玩的?
watchin' out for the Highway Patrol, if you think that's fun.

285
00:24:09,516 --> 00:24:12,977
我得鑽進灌木叢……
God. You know, l hadda go over there in the bushes...

286
00:24:13,061 --> 00:24:17,398
抽根大麻，這樣我才能…你知道嗎?
to smoke a joint, just so l could like-- you know?

287
00:24:17,440 --> 00:24:22,277
對。我在北部有大計劃
Yep. l got somethin' big lined up, up north.

288
00:24:22,319 --> 00:24:26,656
如果沒有我，這些傢伙怎麼可能知道
Yeah, these guys? Wouldn't even fuckin' know about it if it wasn't for me.

289
00:24:26,740 --> 00:24:30,201
- 他一講話我就想揍他 - 他不是問題。
- Every time he opens his mouth, l wanna punch him out. - He's not the problem, Jack.

290
00:24:30,285 --> 00:24:33,246
你幹什麼要把她帶著?
You wanna pull your head outta your ass, tell me why the hell we're bringing her with us?

291
00:24:33,288 --> 00:24:35,540
葛蘭
Glenn.

292
00:24:35,623 --> 00:24:37,916
你不記得我了嗎?
You don't remember me, do you?

293
00:24:39,919 --> 00:24:44,631
我從未進過葛雷茲，如果你是這個意思的話
Um, couldn't have been Glades if that's what you're thinkin', 'cause l was never out there.

294
00:24:44,715 --> 00:24:48,510
- 我不是這個意思 - 是
- No, that's not what I'm thinking. - Oh, yeah?

295
00:24:48,593 --> 00:24:52,096
但你肯定我們見過?
But you're sure we've met, huh?

296
00:24:52,138 --> 00:24:53,847
去年秋天
Last fall.

